1
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:58,599
Kneel.

2
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,239
How long do I have to kneel?

3
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:13,000
Mingcheng, eat something.

4
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,199
Don't starve yourself.

5
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:15,719
You...

6
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:19,000
If you hadn't brought Yang Yunfan into
the Mystic Medicine Association,

7
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,960
would I be stuck eating this slop?

8
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,240
Don't worry.

9
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,120
Father will find a way to get you out.

10
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,120
Get the hell out.

11
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,199
Get out of my sight.

12
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,439
Miss Lu.

13
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:36,919
The Pharmacy Master requests your presence.

14
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:37,719
Alright.

15
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:38,719
Remember this.

16
00:02:38,719 --> 00:02:39,800
Take it away.

17
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,719
Just eat a little.

18
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:42,639
Take it away!

19
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:55,319
Get out!

20
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,400
What a piece of garbage.

21
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,479
They won't get away with messing with me.

22
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:13,000
You shameless little thing.

23
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:15,560
Go flirt with Yang Yunfan some more!

24
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:17,000
Go on!

25
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,280
Now look what's happened.

26
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,919
Your brother got dragged down too.

27
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:24,919
But Mingcheng did do something wrong.

28
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,319
How dare you talk back!

29
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,000
Your brother is the Lu family's future.

30
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,319
Who do you think you are?

31
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:44,360
I'm your daughter.

32
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:46,879
I'm not my brother's accessory.

33
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:48,159
Everything he has now,

34
00:03:48,159 --> 00:03:50,400
I fought to get for him.

35
00:03:53,479 --> 00:03:54,439
It seems you really have been

36
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:56,199
brainwashed by that brat Yang Yunfan.

37
00:03:57,159 --> 00:03:59,240
Defying me for an outsider.

38
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:05,719
I like him.

39
00:04:08,319 --> 00:04:09,400
He's the only one in this world

40
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,759
who recognizes my worth.

41
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,120
Fine.

42
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,800
So you two are that close, huh?

43
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:33,600
Here's the deal.

44
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,680
I'll give you one chance.

45
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,959
Go beg him.

46
00:04:37,959 --> 00:04:39,240
Beg him to spare your brother.

47
00:04:40,319 --> 00:04:42,600
Don't you want to see how much he cares?

48
00:04:43,439 --> 00:04:44,199
Go on!

49
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,079
Since I came down the mountain,

50
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:41,040
you're the first person to be kind to me.

51
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,720
I don't want to see you get hurt.

52
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:52,120
Wu Ming.

53
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,199
I'm begging you.

54
00:05:54,199 --> 00:05:55,639
Please help me, won't you?

55
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,519
How do you want me to help you?

56
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,959
Could you please show mercy

57
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:17,399
and spare my brother?

58
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:22,120
It's not that I don't want to spare them.

59
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:26,519
Your father and your brother,

60
00:06:26,519 --> 00:06:28,199
they treat human lives like dirt.

61
00:06:29,199 --> 00:06:31,399
They toyed with so many people's lives.

62
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,319
But...

63
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:41,519
But if I can't save him,

64
00:06:41,959 --> 00:06:43,959
I really can't go on living.

65
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:46,439
My father will beat me to death.

66
00:06:51,759 --> 00:06:52,439
Tanxiang.

67
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:56,959
You can actually break free from them.

68
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:03,560
That's impossible.

69
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:05,480
I'm a Lu.

70
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,360
I can't escape.

71
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:20,800
You can pretend to be Yang Yunfan
for Ye Qingxue,

72
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,720
so why can't you, for me,

73
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,000
spare my brother?

74
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,040
All this time,

75
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:28,560
I saw you as the only light in my life.

76
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:49,120
My father was right.

77
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:51,959
I overestimated your feelings for me.

78
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:11,480
Mou Ren.

79
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,319
Look at this mess.

80
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:17,360
Pharmacy Master Li.

81
00:08:18,199 --> 00:08:20,519
After all my years of loyalty to you,

82
00:08:20,519 --> 00:08:22,079
I may lack merit, but I've worked hard.

83
00:08:22,079 --> 00:08:23,040
I beg you.

84
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,959
Please save my worthless son.

85
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,600
Haven't I helped you?

86
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,720
If I hadn't helped you,

87
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:32,240
your son wouldn't just be kneeling
before the Medicine Sage.

88
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,120
Yes.

89
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:36,600
Your kindness to us is already immense.

90
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:37,759
But...

91
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:40,159
Mingcheng is the Lu family's only heir!

92
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:16,159
A bad piece should be discarded.

93
00:09:16,159 --> 00:09:18,240
Your son can't even handle a simple task.

94
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,320
He's ruining my grand plan.

95
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,720
Ye Zhentian is already suspicious.

96
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:25,120
Pharmacy Master Li,
your wisdom is unmatched.

97
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,279
You must have another plan up your sleeve.

98
00:09:26,279 --> 00:09:27,320
Just give us the order,

99
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:29,159
and the Lu family will serve you
like beasts of burden.

100
00:09:29,159 --> 00:09:30,519
We'll follow your every command.

101
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:31,720
Even if it costs us our lives,

102
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,559
we won't complain.

103
00:09:39,639 --> 00:09:40,519
Good.

104
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,360
In that case,

105
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:46,240
for the sake of Xiangyang
and Tanxiang's relationship,

106
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:48,679
I'll help you one more time.

107
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:51,639
Thank you, Pharmacy Master Li.

108
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:55,240
Pharmacy Master Li, what should we do?

109
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:55,759
Just give the word.

110
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:02,720
What about my son?

111
00:10:07,639 --> 00:10:10,120
One must know what to sacrifice.

112
00:10:15,639 --> 00:10:16,759
Know what to give up.

113
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:54,240
Miss Ye.

114
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:03,320
So busy, yet you found time to come?

115
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,000
You do it.

116
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:08,879
I don't think that's appropriate.

117
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:11,000
We aren't even married yet,

118
00:11:11,519 --> 00:11:13,279
and you want me playing
the dutiful son already?

119
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:15,720
You should do it.

120
00:11:26,879 --> 00:11:28,799
I know you heard me, so quit pretending.

121
00:11:28,799 --> 00:11:29,879
Sit up a bit and take your medicine.

122
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,159
I never thought

123
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,480
that in this lifetime

124
00:12:45,559 --> 00:12:47,080
I'd see a day like this.

125
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:57,480
Don't flatter yourself.

126
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:59,559
I just worry no one will take care of you.

127
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:09,960
Old Master,

128
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:12,799
stop hiding things from us.

129
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:17,320
If you don't say it now,

130
00:13:18,279 --> 00:13:19,039
you'll never get the chance.

131
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:29,399
How much more are you two hiding from me?

132
00:13:35,799 --> 00:13:37,120
Help me up.

133
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:58,000
Come on in.

134
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:02,799
Stop hiding.

135
00:14:06,639 --> 00:14:10,440
You've been in my study
this whole time, haven't you?

136
00:14:11,919 --> 00:14:14,360
If you'd said you saw me, I wouldn't hide.

137
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:18,720
These poisonous herbs of yours,

138
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,840
you must plan to use them
at the Medicine King Ceremony.

139
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:26,759
How did you know this medicine is toxic?

140
00:14:28,039 --> 00:14:29,159
Never mind how I know.

141
00:14:29,879 --> 00:14:30,960
I actually thought

142
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:34,039
Chief Pharmacist Ye, the last of the
Mystic Medicine Association's
Traditionalist Faction,

143
00:14:34,039 --> 00:14:35,600
would follow the Medicine Sage's teachings

144
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,799
and walk the path of a benevolent healer.

145
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,559
I never expected that at your age,

146
00:14:38,559 --> 00:14:39,759
you'd still use poison to harm people.

147
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,679
I was right about you.

148
00:14:50,639 --> 00:14:53,759
Mingyuan's son is just like him,

149
00:14:53,759 --> 00:14:54,879
an upright man.

150
00:14:56,679 --> 00:14:58,440
How did you know who I am?

151
00:14:58,440 --> 00:15:01,120
Song Ci confirmed it through
the birthmark on your body.

152
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:08,000
Don't distract me with this nonsense.

153
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:10,360
I can't let you use these poisons
to harm people.

154
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,279
Come in.

155
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,840
There's something you don't know.

156
00:15:24,919 --> 00:15:26,240
Ten years ago,

157
00:15:27,039 --> 00:15:28,480
a strange disease broke out.

158
00:15:29,039 --> 00:15:30,440
my wife unfortunately fell ill.

159
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:33,399
I was truly powerless back then.

160
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:35,919
I could only watch helplessly as she

161
00:15:35,919 --> 00:15:37,559
grew weaker, little by little,

162
00:15:37,559 --> 00:15:38,720
until in the end,

163
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:41,399
she passed away.

164
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:43,559
Daddy,

165
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:46,679
when will Mommy get better?

166
00:15:58,799 --> 00:15:59,799
Sweetheart,

167
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:02,519
go pour your mom a glass of water.

168
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:23,320
Mom, you're going to get better.

169
00:16:24,879 --> 00:16:25,679
Good girl.

170
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,159
There's a way.

171
00:16:42,559 --> 00:16:43,840
There has to be a way.

172
00:16:58,679 --> 00:17:01,279
I'm a bastard. I'm a fool.

173
00:17:02,639 --> 00:17:05,480
I've studied medicine for decades,

174
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:07,640
yet I can't even cure my own wife.

175
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:10,519
What kind of doctor am I?

176
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:26,680
Wanning.

177
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:27,920
Drink the medicine.

178
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,039
You'll be better soon.

179
00:17:29,039 --> 00:17:29,920
Chief Pharmacist Ye.

180
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:32,519
Chief Pharmacist Ye.

181
00:17:33,359 --> 00:17:34,519
Chief Pharmacist Ye.

182
00:17:34,519 --> 00:17:36,160
Sorry to intrude.

183
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:41,759
This can cure Mrs. Ye's illness.

184
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:45,000
What kind of medicine is this?

185
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:48,359
The latest tech from Heqian Pharma in Wo.

186
00:17:48,359 --> 00:17:49,519
Cures any disease, guaranteed.

187
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:57,319
No medicine in this world cures all.

188
00:17:59,079 --> 00:18:00,000
Cheng Qi.

189
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:01,880
Show him out.

190
00:18:04,359 --> 00:18:06,640
Uncle Lu, can you save my mom?

191
00:18:06,640 --> 00:18:08,720
Please, I'm begging you, save her.

192
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:10,200
Of course. This medicine can do it.

193
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:11,400
Qingxue.

194
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:12,319
Move aside.

195
00:18:14,559 --> 00:18:15,359
Let me tell you something.

196
00:18:16,319 --> 00:18:17,799
Even if my wife dies,

197
00:18:18,319 --> 00:18:21,519
I won't use your phony tech-made drugs.

198
00:18:22,559 --> 00:18:23,680
Show him out.

199
00:18:24,519 --> 00:18:25,799
Why are you being so stubborn?

200
00:18:25,799 --> 00:18:26,920
This is advanced technology.

201
00:18:26,920 --> 00:18:28,079
High tech, I tell you!

202
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:30,079
You're a bad man!

203
00:18:30,079 --> 00:18:32,039
You don't even want to save Mom!

204
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:54,200
So...

205
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:59,079
you found out the Tech Faction's medicine
was tainted back then,

206
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:02,599
which is why you didn't give it to Mom?

207
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:06,400
In this world,

208
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:09,240
there's no such thing as a cure-all.

209
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:13,240
Unless it was a conspiracy from the start.

210
00:19:14,759 --> 00:19:15,759
My child,

211
00:19:17,559 --> 00:19:21,200
I couldn't gamble with your mother's life.

212
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,960
So all these years,

213
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:27,960
you had to bear it all alone?

214
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:31,640
You silly old man.

215
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:44,240
Good child.

216
00:19:46,599 --> 00:19:47,680
You're so silly.

217
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:01,519
These two...

218
00:20:08,519 --> 00:20:11,440
Brother Mingyuan had just found a clue,

219
00:20:12,119 --> 00:20:13,039
and the Yang family

220
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:16,160
was wiped out.

221
00:20:18,039 --> 00:20:20,079
I will definitely

222
00:20:20,079 --> 00:20:22,039
make them pay the price.

223
00:20:24,480 --> 00:20:25,880
Oh, you're here.

224
00:20:25,880 --> 00:20:26,640
What?

225
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,920
The father and daughter just made up.

226
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:28,920
Give them some space.

227
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:31,799
But there's a situation right now.

228
00:20:31,799 --> 00:20:34,079
The strange illness from back then
reappeared at the Medicine King Ceremony.

229
00:20:34,079 --> 00:20:35,519
They claim the poisoned herbs

230
00:20:35,519 --> 00:20:37,720
came from the Qingmu Hall's storehouse.

231
00:20:37,720 --> 00:20:39,960
Now they've brought people
to confront us.

232
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:41,640
Given the old master's condition...

233
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:43,000
The old master can't handle the shock.

234
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:43,720
Right.

235
00:20:43,720 --> 00:20:44,720
I'll handle it.

236
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:45,799
I'll deal with it as it comes.
